<br>
Having just reached 16 I have been looking for Tasarin's Grimoire pg 26 left and right sides for the mesmerization spell.<br>
<br>
I have been looking in the bazaar all weekend and have only seen 2 half page 26's. One guy wanted 500pp the other guy wanted 3000pp! WTF? 3000pp for half a page for a lowly level 16 spell? <br>
<br>
Are these greedy people out of their minds? Where do they get the idea a level 16 could afford this? I guess they assume everyone is a twink and can farm stuff for the cash with their high level character? <br>
<br>
Is it normal for people to price gouge for pg 26?<br>
<br>
Where is a good place for me to find these on my own in a reasonable amount of time? Should I just use my BL to kill masses of 16-20 mobs somewhere? <br>
<br>
Is this page so rare that I would be wasting my time trying to get it on my own? Should I just forget about it and wait for a higher level spell? I could get to 24 in PC in a matter of hours so I wonder if I should just forget this spell.<br>
<br>
I just want to get the Mesmerization spell so I can be more effective in a group. It seems to me this is a must have spell, CC being an Enchanters main role.<br>
<br>
If there are any Enchanters on Quellious (sp?) that have an extra lev 16 mesmerization spell they could sell cheap/donate I would greatly appreciate it. My chanters name is Zacula.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jabarivoodoo>Jabari Voodoo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#330000>(9/2/03 6:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=310.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Price gouging for lev 16 pages?</span><hr size=1> Wow! I saw pg 26 in Bazaar for 50pp and thought that was over priced.<br>
